	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ну почему <tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /> не <anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />может
